result.title: BaseAuthenticator
result.description: An implementation of okhttp3.Authenticator, which can be used to authenticate every REST request.

result.title: BaseInterceptor
result.description: An implementation of okhttp3.Interceptor, which can be used to modify every ongoing REST Request.

result.title: CacheInterceptor
result.description: An implementation of BaseInterceptor, which applies Cache Control to every ongoing REST request.

result.title: DataStorePreference
result.description: A wrapper of DataStore of type Preference, fulfills the purpose of storing/retrieving the Data from the Persistence Storage.

result.title: BaseModel
result.description: A Class that encapsulates common data related to UI which is used between BaseActivity and BaseViewModel.

result.title: BaseRepository
result.description: A Class that encapsulates the common set-up required to set-up a Repository.

result.title: BaseViewModel
result.description: A Class that encapsulates the common set-up required to set-up a androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel.

result.title: BaseViewModel
result.description: An extension of ViewModel to contain the common methods related to Controlling View as well as Data.

result.title: ViewModelKey
result.description: An Annotation of type dagger.MapKey which is used to inject the ViewModel using Dagger.

result.title: VMFactory
result.description: An extension of androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelProvider.Factory which is generic in nature and is used to supply ViewModel.

result.title: BaseActivity
result.description: An extension of androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity with code set-up along with BaseModel, BaseViewModel, and the Data Binding Class required for an Activity.

result.title: BaseSingleVHAdapter
result.description: An extension of androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter with code set-up along with BaseViewModel, to support a RecyclerView.Adapter with a single type of RecyclerView.ViewHolder.

result.title: BaseMultipleVHAdapter
result.description: An extension of androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter, to support a RecyclerView.Adapter with a multiple types of RecyclerView.ViewHolder.

result.title: BaseBottomSheetDialog
result.description: An extension of com.google.android.material.bottomsheet.BottomSheetDialogFragment, as an customized Bottom Sheet Dialog with all the set-up done.

result.title: BaseDialogFragment
result.description: An extension of androidx.fragment.app.DialogFragment, as an customized Dialog Fragment with all the set-up done.

result.title: BaseFragment
result.description: An extension of androidx.fragment.app.Fragment, as an customized Fragment with all the set-up done.

result.title: BaseFragmentListener
result.description: An Interface with common abstract methods required by a BaseFragment.

result.title: PopUpWindow
result.description: A wrapper class that contains implementation of android.widget.PopupWindow to show a Pop-Up Window in the UI.

result.title: BaseViewHolder
result.description: An extension of androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder with all the set-up done, as well as it is Lifecycle Aware.

result.title: DefaultMessages.kt
result.description: An extension of androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder with all the set-up done, as well as it is Lifecycle Aware.
